    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cf953754c2c0b82f4cb3003"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "And the last part would be an invitation to meet the sender at [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreEspia],Espia]]? \n\nAnd what happens if we run into the real Banshees instead?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
