        "id": "9ce3f0b65589934eb98d11a8"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "But can we? If someone has located us, how long until the Taurians or someone else will? \n\nThis posing as Jinxie act is not going to last much longer. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Eventually we will need another sponsor like Interstellar Expeditions.",
