      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c1616c860cfa19d7b08a013"
      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "And if it's the Combine, they might treat mercenaries poorly but at the same time we're too far away for them to try to pull [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreCompanyStore],company store]] type tactics. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "What do you think, captain?",
          "conditions": null,
